1599451200.title: CNN Newsroom
1599451200.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1599458400.title: CNN Newsroom with Kim Brunhuber
1599458400.descr: Live from Atlanta, Kim Brunhuber brings context and clarity to the day's top stories from around the world.

1599469200.title: Early Start
1599469200.descr: Early Start is a hard news morning television show on CNN anchored by Christine Romans and Laura Jarrett, aired weekdays. Keep up with the latest news and top stories of the day, stay tuned for all important events on the global arena.

1599472800.title: New Day
1599472800.descr: Alisyn Camerota and John Berman report the latest news and top stories.

1599483600.title: First Move with Julia Chatterley
1599483600.descr: First Move is a business news show,broadcast live daily from the floor of the New York Stock Exchange. The host of the show is Julia Chatterley, a global market analyst, an anchor and correspondent for CNN. The show highlights top stories in the world of business and money. Be the first to know the news influencing global politics, culture and finance.

1599487200.title: Connect the World
1599487200.descr: Join high profile news anchor Becky Anderson live from Abu Dhabi as she brings you all the latest news from around the world . This is CNN's international flagship current affairs prime time news program.

1599501600.title: Amanpour
1599501600.descr: Christiane Amanpour provides her powerful interview skills and provocative analysis on global stories that matter to you.

1599505200.title: Quest Means Business
1599505200.descr: He's not messing around: Richard Quest presents his hot takes on the biggest breaking stories in the world of business. Watch for the expert analysis, commentary and opinions on the important headlines in the field from the notorious English journalist and CNN anchor. Joined by a cast of experts and correspondents delivering unrivaled facts on everything going down in the world of business.

1599508800.title: The Lead with Jake Tapper
1599508800.descr: Current affairs programme hosted by the journalist and author, Jake Tapper. Jake Tapper is the chief Washington correspondent for CNN and he will share his knowledge and insight into politics as well as covering a variety of other topics. This programme discusses a range of stories from topical events including national news, economics/finance, sports, health, technology and world affairs.

1599512400.title: The Situation Room
1599512400.descr: Wolf Blitzer is in the command center for breaking news, politics and extraordinary reports from around the world.

1599519600.title: Erin Burnett OutFront
1599519600.descr: Hosted by Erin Burnett, OutFront is an hour-long news programme examining the latest stories from the US and further afield. The show features insightful opinions from informed guests, leaving no stone unturned.

1599523200.title: TBD
1599523200.descr: The latest news, the biggest stories. CNN brings viewers coverage of the most gripping news stories from around the world.
